5&amp;resize=1224%2C811 3x\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/05_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-14271d3.png?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C368, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/05_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-14271d3.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C736 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/05_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-14271d3.png?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C368, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/05_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-14271d3.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C736 2x\" type=\"image/png\"><img class=\"wp-image-622971 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/05_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-14271d3.png?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C411\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Smart Tire Company Metl airless tyre\" title=\"Smart Tire Company Metl airless tyre\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Though they’ve only been shown on a road bike, STC expects to see the tyres used on mountain bikes as well.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Smart Tire Company</i></span></div>\n<p>Though the press images only show a slick tyre, the brand is pitching the tyre as suitable for road, gravel, mountain and ebike applications.</p>\n<p>The press pack for the tyre does not specify whether the tyre fits like a standard clincher or a tubular, but the images included show it fitted to an otherwise normal looking deep-section wheel, suggesting nothing out of the ordinary is going on.</p>\n<p>Felt Bicycles is supplying test bikes to STC and will be involved as a development partner. The company also has an existing relationship with Spin, a bike and scooter-sharing company owned by Ford.</p>\n<p>While the Metl tyre technology will debut on bicycles, there are intentions for it to break into the “auto industry and beyond”.</p>\n<h2>How much will the tyres weigh and what do they ride like?</h2>\n<div class=\"image-handler__container image-handler__container--full\" style=\"padding-bottom: calc(100% * (946 / 1423));\">\n    <picture><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C598 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1200%2C798 4x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(max-width: 320px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=90&amp;resize=300%2C199, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=600%2C399 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=900%2C598 3x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/produ