atile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C412, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1240%2C824 2x\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C542 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C814 3x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 768px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=90&amp;resize=408%2C271, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=816%2C542 2x, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1224%2C814 3x\" type=\"image/png\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?webp=true&amp;quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C739 2x\" type=\"image/webp\"><source media=\"(min-width: 590px)\" data-srcset=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=90&amp;resize=556%2C370, https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=45&amp;resize=1112%2C739 2x\" type=\"image/png\"><img class=\"wp-image-622969 align size-landscape_thumbnail image-handler__image image-handler__image--full no-wrap js-lazyload\" data-src=\"https://images.immediate.co.uk/production/volatile/sites/21/2021/03/03_smart_tire_compant_metl_airless_tyre-52ae1c4.png?quality=90&amp;resize=620%2C412\" width=\"620\" height=\"413\" alt=\"Smart Tire Company Metl airless tyre\" title=\"Smart Tire Company Metl airless tyre\"></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></source></picture></div><div class=\"caption-hold\"><figcaption class=\"wp-caption-text\"><span class=\"caption-copy\"><i class=\"icon-arrow icon-camera-circle\"></i> Testing indicates the tyres ride much like a normal tyre.</span></figcaption><span class=\"im-image-caption\"> <i>Smart Tire Company</i></span></div>\n<p>There is no claimed weight for the Metl tyre, but the STC website claims the system is “competitive with many mainstream alternatives”.</p>\n<p>The other key question is whether the tyre will present an increase in rolling resistance compared to a traditional rubber tyre.</p>\n<p>According to STC, a prototype version of the tyre that was built to simulate a standard pneumatic tyre inflated to 100psi has been ridden by the test team and the difference between the Metl tyre and a pneumatic tyre was “not noticeable”.</p>\n<h2>When will these tyres be available and how much will they cost?</h2>\n<p>The press release for the tyres included no further information on expected availability, projected pricing or in-depth technical details.</p>\n<p>We have contacted SMART Tire Company for further details and will update this article once we hear back. In the meantime, let us know if you have any further questions in the comments.</p>","author":"Jack Luke","siteTitle":"BikeRadar","siteHash":"df99dd1320fcd97327a2def4c67247c08cd4090a7dab684a0eddb9b856f80ef1","entryHash":"50f5c418564e806d2ec9f46c882c04cdc3fddfebf39bd6c287b34183acc26872","category":"Cycling"}